name: e2e-automation-playwright-ts
description: Requirements to run successfully this project: - Node.js 18+ - Windows 10+, Windows Server 2016+ or Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL). - MacOS 12 Monterey, MacOS 13 Ventura, or MacOS 14 Sonoma. - Debian 11, Debian 12, Ubuntu 20.04 or Ubuntu 22.04, with x86-64 or arm64 architecture.
